**The Role**

Bolt is seeking an experienced **Construction Site Superintendent** to oversee day-to-day field operations on **New York City–based** hospitality, retail, and residential projects. This is a hands-on, site-first role for someone who knows how to run a clean, safe, well-coordinated job site and take pride in the details.

